    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p><strong>Requirements </strong>You are holding a Ghostfire Vial</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count:1\">            </span>You throw your Ghostfire Vial and channel ether into it, casting it farther as it violently explodes and rains down crawling, searing flame. Spectral blue fire cascades and whirls in the area of the burst, remaining in the spot and burning creatures that stand within it.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count:1\">            </span>Any creatures who begin their turn or enter the area need to make a basic Fortitude save or take 4d6 spirit damage and 2d6 persistent spirit damage.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Heightened</strong>(+2): The spirit damage and persistent spirit damage increases by 2d6.</p>"
